{"type":null,"faqId":49480,"title":"剪辑视频","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:13pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"视频趣味剪辑\"XE \"编辑视频\"XE \"剪辑视频\"XE \"剪辑本地视频\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189281\" style=\"width:0.24583334in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“视频”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>在“我的”页签下，选择要剪辑的本地视频。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 3  </span><span>点击要剪辑视频旁边的“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189282\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，然后点击“视频趣味剪辑”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 4  </span><span>按照界面提示对视频进行剪辑。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 5  </span><span>剪辑完成后，点击“保存”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>后续处理</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189283\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>您也可以在“图库”中选择要剪辑的视频，然后点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189284\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，按照界面提示对视频进行剪辑。</span>\n</p>\n<br>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1089,"faqType":"音乐与视频","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5224","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Music-Video","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447294370000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":61,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}